In The Dinner Project, passionate home cook Hayden Quinn travels the country to meet every day Australians from all walks of life and inspires them to create fresh, simple and healthy meals at home. Hayden will live the life of each of his hosts to gain an insight into their daily routine and the challenges they face in getting healthy home-cooked meals on the table.
